<br>
In Group: Yes<br>
In Zone: Yes<br>
Range: 10000 feet<br>
<br>
There are some zones in which CoH is disabled or &quot;changed&quot; such as Plane of Sky, some parts of Plane of Nightmare, Acrylia Caverns, etc.<br>
<br>
Generally i used it to speed up travelling of raid members (such as in WW going to ToV, ferry clerics across dangerous territories, etc). Rescue a monk/SK FD'd on a bad pull or simply Summon raid members to safe spot, etc.<br>
